description: [``botocore``] This release adds log APIs that allow customers to manage logging for their Amazon Managed Service for Prometheus workspaces.
[``botocore``] The Amazon Chime SDK now supports channels with up to one million participants with elastic channels.
[``botocore``] Updates various list api MaxResults ranges
[``botocore``] This release provides support for promotions in AWS Personalize runtime.
[``botocore``] Adds support for RDS Custom to DBInstanceClass in ModifyDBInstance
